. Our algorithm has space and time complexity $poly(n,2^{5.6n},d)$\n(or $poly(n^{\\log n},2^{5.6n},d)$ under some weaker assumptions).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2021 18:13:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Oct 2021 18:15:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 19:02:04 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sun, 20 Mar 2022 22:33:31 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2022 18:03:12 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2022 10:16:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
