med. We use our unique biographical,\nadministrative, publication, and citation database ('Polish Science\nObservatory') with metadata on all Polish scientists present in Scopus\n(N=25,463) and their 158,743 Scopus-indexed articles published in 2009-2018,\nincluding 18,900 solo articles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Jan 2021 20:52:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 27 Sep 2021 06:08:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 5 Mar 2022 19:26:05 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 8 May 2023 04:51:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-09"}
